flowchart TB
    %% COMPONENT: Guidance Self-Review Loop
    %% PURPOSE: Iterative guidance improvement through agent self-review
    %% USAGE: Planners include this when planning guidance improvements for multiple agents
    %% LOOP TYPE: guidance-test-loop (iterate until agents report no issues)
    %%
    %% PATTERN SUMMARY:
    %% 1. Target agents self-review their own guidance (parallel)
    %% 2. Collect questions/issues requiring user decisions
    %% 3. User provides answers to ambiguities
    %% 4. planner-guidance creates remediation plans (parallel)
    %% 5. teacher-update-guidance executes fixes
    %% 6. Loop back until multiple agents report "NO ISSUES REMAINING"

    %% ===== PHASE 1: SELF-REVIEW =====
    LoopStart((Guidance Self-Review Loop)) --> IdentifyTargets[Identify Target Agents from Plan]

    IdentifyTargets --> SpawnSelfReview["Spawn Target Agents (Parallel)
    Task: Self-review own guidance files
    - inputs.yml
    - process.yml
    - manifest.yml"]

    %% Self-review outputs
    SpawnSelfReview --> CollectResults[Collect Self-Review Results]

    CollectResults --> AnalyzeResults{Issues Found?}

    %% No issues = exit loop
    AnalyzeResults -- "No Issues from Multiple Agents" --> LoopComplete((Loop Complete: Guidance Validated))

    %% ===== PHASE 2: USER DECISION GATE =====
    AnalyzeResults -- "Issues/Questions Found" --> ConsolidateQuestions[Consolidate Questions by Theme]

    ConsolidateQuestions --> UserDecisionGate{Questions for User?}

    UserDecisionGate -- "Yes" --> PresentQuestions["Present Questions to User
    - Group by theme
    - Provide options where applicable
    - Allow clarification input"]

    PresentQuestions --> AwaitAnswers[/User Provides Answers/]

    AwaitAnswers --> RecordDecisions[Record User Decisions]

    UserDecisionGate -- "No (Clear fixes)" --> RecordDecisions

    %% ===== PHASE 3: REMEDIATION PLANNING =====
    RecordDecisions --> SpawnPlannerGuidance["Spawn planner-guidance Agents (Parallel)
    One per target agent with issues
    Inputs: issues + user decisions"]

    SpawnPlannerGuidance --> PlansCreated{Plans Created?}

    PlansCreated -- "Error" --> EscalatePlanning((Escalate: Planning Failed))

    PlansCreated -- "Yes" --> CollectPlans["Collect Remediation Plans
    Output: plan_guidance_<agent>.yml files"]

    %% ===== PHASE 4: EXECUTION =====
    CollectPlans --> ReviewPlans{Plans Approved?}

    ReviewPlans -- "No" --> EscalatePlanning

    ReviewPlans -- "Yes" --> SpawnTeachers["Spawn teacher-update-guidance Agents
    Execute tasks from remediation plans"]

    SpawnTeachers --> FixesApplied[Fixes Applied to Guidance Files]

    %% ===== LOOP BACK =====
    FixesApplied --> IncrementIteration[Increment Iteration Counter]

    IncrementIteration --> CheckMaxIterations{Max Iterations Reached?}

    CheckMaxIterations -- "No" --> SpawnSelfReview

    CheckMaxIterations -- "Yes (3)" --> EscalateMaxIterations((Escalate: Max Iterations Reached))

    %% ===== STYLING =====
    classDef entrypoint fill:#90EE90,stroke:#228B22
    classDef exitpoint fill:#FFB6C1,stroke:#DC143C
    classDef usergate fill:#87CEEB,stroke:#4169E1
    classDef parallel fill:#DDA0DD,stroke:#8B008B

    class LoopStart,LoopComplete entrypoint
    class EscalatePlanning,EscalateMaxIterations exitpoint
    class PresentQuestions,AwaitAnswers usergate
    class SpawnSelfReview,SpawnPlannerGuidance,SpawnTeachers parallel
